{"tid":851841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港] 塞車等紅燈太無聊　後座正妹「偷玩海鮮」被抓包","createTime":"2018-10-07T12:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T13:40:14.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"38f0672880e9fa882e9ae279b17eff648cdda7c9","tid":851841,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"自娛娛人！香港一名網友日前搭小巴出遊碰上堵車，等紅燈時太無聊拿起手機亂拍，沒想到意外捕捉到隔壁計程車後座的正妹左手一邊在下體遊移、右手一邊玩手機，看的他是目瞪口呆、啞口無言，忍不住驚呼，「現在的女生都那麼開放嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n後來這段影片在《WhatsApp》香港地區群組瘋傳，不過也有網友看完之後覺得沒什麼，「就跟男生有時候老二癢一樣嘛，難免忍不住就想抓一下啊」、「說不定是在調整內褲，拍攝影片的人是不是想太多了？」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181007/1443550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181007%2F1443550&d=4xkOgrXO0dUXB3S%2FBHQ4Hf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=50434035\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181007%2F1443550&h=afe7b686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181007/1443550</a>"},{"pid":"4bade9d851b0c2fedffb4ead2c9740c1058ed428","tid":851841,"uid":1367,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:30:22.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"0d4c130f26cb00571b28d13f39e2f14e90fd2eb3","tid":851841,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d9c6164e8af4334d6170f55efbef527245ed8f","tid":851841,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4bade9d851b0c2fedffb4ead2c9740c1058ed428","tid":851841,"uid":1367,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:30:22.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:31:07.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"634718cf1ccd76d0e8820f2c8657ffed9791f183","tid":851841,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,